1. Ja volim da *plešem* sa prijateljima. (I like to dance with friends.)
2. Oni su sinoć *plesali* na rođendanskoj proslavi. (They danced at the birthday party last night.)
3. Ti bi trebalo da *plešeš* na pozornici sa ostalim plesačima. (You should dance on stage with the other dancers.)
4. Ona je već nekoliko sati *plesala* i umorna je. (She has been dancing for several hours and is tired.)
5. Kada sam čuo tu pesmu, poželeo sam da *plešem* sa tobom. (When I heard that song, I wanted to dance with you.)
6. Moja sestra *pleše* balet već pet godina. (My sister has been dancing ballet for five years.)
7. Da li bi volela da *plešeš* sa mnom? (Would you like to dance with me?)
8. Pogledaj kako *plešu* mladi parovi na podijumu. (Look at how the young couples are dancing on the dance floor.)
9. Nikada nisam znao da li je bolje *plesati* sam ili u paru. (I never knew if it was better to dance alone or with a partner.)
10. Oni će *plesati* valcer na svom venčanju. (They will dance the waltz at their wedding.)